Used to specify one or more folders on the device to monitor for changes, including folders in protected areas of an Android device. **Folder(s) specified in this parameter _replace_ any previously specified folder(s)**. To add a folder to an existing folder list, specify the entire (comma-separated) list including the new folder. 

**This parameter does not detect Threats**. 

**Parm value input rules**:

* String from 1 - 255 characters containing comma-separated list of fully qualified path(s) to folder(s) on the device. **Replaces any previously specified folder list.**  
